Title: [ANN][AirDrop][ICO]Water 2 The World ICO Airdrop Contest Details
Body: Thanks to everyone who is supporting the project , we have completed Phase 1 of the airdrop with over 30 Million tokens going out to more than 6,000 supporters from our whitelist, Please post your ERC20 Wallet address here if you did not get your tokens and we will check into it for you and send you the tokens.  Great news in that we have the tokens listed on a few exchanges already. Goto Token Jar, Forkdelta or any of the De-centralized exchanges and enter the:  Contract Code: 0xC963bA763211B28dBB1ACD7782d639ce5F42B85a Token Symbol: W2TW Decimals: 18  To begin trading your tokens. We will have updates on the project and the release of the prototype video in the next few weeks. Also the final Tally for the Bounty Campaign will be announced before July 15, 2018 with over 1.5 Million USD still to be given in W2TW tokens. Thanks Again from the Water2 The World Team

Author: Blockvisory
Title: [ANN][AirDrop][ICO]Water 2 The World ICO Airdrop Contest Details
Body: The smartmachine will be available for purchase by anyone, we will have a low cost affordable version for small households and after R&D the plan is to have larger scaled up version for industrial, disaster and government use. The cost to produce each smartmachine is not available at this time, this is why we are raising funds to complete the R&D. The price points have not been determined at this point either, the goal of the first phase R&D is to be able to produce the smartmachines at the lowest cost and with the most efficient materials. The token will appreciate in value from the demand for the Atmospheric data that will be mined/collected by each smartmachine. The ideal is to have several hundred thousand of the smartmachines spread globally to give true unbiased research to the exact state of the earth's environment worldwide. I hope this helps you understand our project better, we have the proof of concept prototype currently being enhanced by the founder and his assistants in Arkansas, USA and the patent has been applied for in the US as well.  we have known that this project should we get the funding we are seeking, will be world changing and have the biggest social impact of any blockchain project out there..  Please continue to follow us on Facebook and Telegram for more updates...

Author: Apekool
Title: [ANN][AirDrop][ICO]Water 2 The World ICO Airdrop Contest Details
Body: I'm still going through the white paper, but a question in the mean time;     I know that you're current phase is still R&D, but there's an existing problem with the process as described that isn't solved.  During the process of evaporation or distillation of liquid water, the water molecules will go through a phase transition and expand in volume as it becomes a gas. As a gas nothing can be dissolved in the water. Separating the gas molecules of water from the other molecules that were previously dissolved in the liquid water removes all non-water molecules from the equation, effectively "purifying" the water. However would condensation then take place the net result would be distilled water.  It would be pretty ingenious if you get that technique from the article to work efficiently in a machine the size of a suitcase.  However the problem I mentioned is about the end product. Condensation of water vapor in a controlled environment might give you liquid water, but it is not just the water molecules that make drinking water. There has to be an addition of electrolytes and minerals, because in the physiology of the human body there is a strict relation between the osmotic gradient of any taken fluid, the amount of fluid taken, and the chance of surviving that.  This would imply that each machine holds somekind of a module or a cartridge in which those elektrolytes and minerals are stored?  So what happens for example when the machine runs out of electrolyte and mineral additives?

Author: Blockvisory
Title: [ANN][AirDrop][ICO]Water 2 The World ICO Airdrop Contest Details
Body: Great point, I will forward this question to the founder, I believe that he is aware of this concern and will test different solutions to this problem during the R&D phase of the project.  Thanks for the inquiry.  Water2theworld team

Author: mgieringer
Title: [ANN][AirDrop][ICO]Water 2 The World ICO Airdrop Contest Details
Body: Hello all, this is the "guy in the video." Yep, I'm a real, normal person, nothing to hide. It's true, the White paper has less marketing talk than most of these offerings because I believe you should pitch what you are sure of, and not marketing hype. So we're working on keeping this real.  Regarding the electrolyte question, yes, those are important for our bodies. Water is not the only source of electrolytes, and the commenter was exactly correct - the end product of our process will be pure water. Our formal research and development effort will determine what, if any, additives may be needed to provide a balance of minerals - in essence, restoring impurities to the water.
